text: FK 14 Oktomvri 1946 () is a football club based in the village of Krupište near Štip, North Macedonia. They currently play in the Macedonian Third League. ==References== == External links == *14 Oktomvri 1946 Facebook *Club info at MacedonianFootball *Football Federation of Macedonia Category:Football clubs in North Macedonia Category:Karbinci Municipality
